@10190 = ~Jack Of All Trades~
@10191 = ~This rare and wonderful cloak goes by the name Jack. Originally worn by Dapper Jack, he was a peasant who grew up with nothing but an incredible will to become anything and everything. He had heard tales that Elminster, the Sage, had throughout his long life, many professions and many careers before ending up as Mystra's archmage. Dapper Jack went through life learning the finesse of a thief, the style of a fighter, the devotion of a cleric, and the determination of a mage before eventually creating this item at the end years of his own long life. It was said to strike awe into those around him, and the experience of his long years was woven into its thread and beating with a life all their own.

